high_descs: Move to the metal rack right of the sink.
Pick up the sponge from the rack.
Bring the sponge to the sink.
Wet the sponge in the sink.
Bring the sponge to the metal rack.
But the sponge on the metal rack.
anns.task_desc: Put a wet sponge on the metal rack.

high_descs: Walk forward, then left towards the sink.
Take green sponge from the rack on the right.
Turn left and face the sink on from the left side.
Wash sponge in the sink and take it out.
Turn right and walk left to face the rack.
Put the green sponge back on the rack.
anns.task_desc: Wash a sponge in the sink.

high_descs: Cross the room to the toilet, turn left, and cross the room to the steel rack.
Pick up the sponge.
Turn around, cross the room to the tub, and turn around to face the sink.
Put the sponge in the sink, turn the water on, turn the water off, and pick up the sponge.
Cross the room to the door and turn left.
Put the sponge on the steel rack.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean sponge on the steel rack.

high_descs: Move across the room to the silver shelves to the right of the sink
Pick up the green sponge on the lower shelf
Carry the green sponge to the sink
Place the sponge in the sink and turn the sink on then turn it off
Carry the sponge back to the shelf
Place the sponge on the second shelf from the top
anns.task_desc: clean and return a sponge to the shelf
